* SAMCode v0.1-alpha / EvenOrOdd
* Ask for a number
	write Tell me a number:
* Take in input
	input as num: number
* Create a num that will be 0 if even
	num remainder: number % 2
* Check if even
	if remainder = 0:
		write (number) is even!
		endif
	if remainder != 0:
		write (number) is odd!
		endif